  "reference_number": "CTD0009",
  "remarks": "\nHMT has reasonable grounds to suspect that the Kieran Gallagher is an involved person under the Counter-Terrorism (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis that he has been, and is, involved in terrorist activity on the basis that:\n(1) Gallagher is and has been involved in terrorist activity by providing financial services, or making available funds or economic resources, for the purposes of terrorism; and \n(2) Gallagher is and has been involved in terrorist activity by facilitating terrorism. \n",
